content.text: This is the story is the rollout for the 2 stories
and CP-414.
The challenges we are going to face with this is that not every repo has a buildspec, not every repo has a artifact storage bucket, so really, this story breaks down to the following tasks:
1. Go through each repo and check what it has / what is missing
2. Update the code or the lz-provisioning code to add what is missing if required
3. Update/Add the `buildspec.yml` and the `Makefile` for releasing
